    { "text": "Cette entreprise veut {1} de nouveaux marchés.", "blanks": [ { "cue": "to develop", "answer": ["développer"] } ], "explanation": "développer = to develop (infinitive)." },
    { "text": "Le débat a soulevé un vrai {1}.", "blanks": [ { "cue": "problem", "answer": ["problème"] } ], "explanation": "problème = problem (masculine)." },
    { "text": "Nous cherchons une {1} durable.", "blanks": [ { "cue": "solution", "answer": ["solution"] } ], "explanation": "solution = solution (feminine)." },
